{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083070/extras/Logogif.gif?t=1728898792\" />Welcome to a simulator where one decision can be the last and the line between life &amp; death is thin.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u>A brief description of the profession of Sapper: unforgiving, underpaid, working under constant stress and in difficult conditions.</u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083070/extras/Command.gif?t=1728898792\" /><strong>Remember you don't do this job for fame, relaxation, or money. You are here to save lives. Show you have the guts and enlist now.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083070/extras/Wishlist.gif?t=1728898792\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>HERE ARE THE THING YOU WILL DO AS A SAPPER:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>WORKING IN DIFFERENT LOCATIONS</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083070/extras/Places.gif?t=1728898792\" />You shouldn't get bored here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>SEARCHING</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083070/extras/Searching.gif?t=1728898792\" />There are tons of places to search for the bombs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>LOCKPICKING</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083070/extras/Lockpicking.gif?t=1728898792\" />There are many locked doors, but that can't stop you from saving lives, right?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>HACKING</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083070/extras/Hacking.gif?t=1728898792\" />It's good that you haven't spent all your time on games using your PC.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>TRAINING</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083070/extras/Training.gif?t=1728898792\" />A rookie without training is a dead rookie.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>WORKING UNDER PRESSURE OF TIME</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083070/extras/Pressure.gif?t=1728898792\" />Nerves of steel are a must in this job. No shaky hands.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>FINDING THE BOMBS</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083070/extras/Finding.gif?t=1728898792\" />If you want to defuse the bomb, first you need to find it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong> DEFUSING THE BOMBS AND MINES</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083070/extras/Disarming.gif?t=1728898792\" />Now here is where the real &quot;fun&quot; starts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Are you willing to take on one of the most dangerous jobs in human history! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Check what kind of bombs you will need to defuse first.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083070/extras/Bombs.png?t=1728898792\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Stay safe, and save the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1083070/extras/Save_the_world.gif?t=1728898792\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Share your opinion with us on the special discord channel.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"YOLO, cut the red","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1083070/9fe26890eb64034955aa9b3969d0cf9c743de790.jpg"},{"name":"Mine Specialist","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1083070/1cdd761272a021fdba9db96aea7c118f8fb819d9.jpg"},{"name":"Short fuse!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1083070/61bc74b2f680be410cf26d1b82e6ca923affee04.jpg"},{"name":"Are you shining for me or for yourself?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1083070/0f3d2b87fbcb6dd83d71b8cbcdc529adc765276c.jpg"},{"name":"PARKOUR, PARKOUR, YEAH!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1083070/7acecb998aaa77618d15610c435fc1547a7ae579.jpg"},{"name":"Hackerman","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1083070/8334d655d00944b66b70138fffad6a9dcd55a852.jpg"},{"name":"Practice makes perfect","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1083070/185ced7e9d57ebb2159d7f743a137bd98847dde7.jpg"},{"name":"Renaissance Sapper ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1083070/cb42557ad4ae789deb3edb4f9c20b58bd4985cf6.jpg"},{"name":"Greenhorn","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1083070/e95f22dad19ec561cdd1f04924c767c90d34cb55.jpg"},{"name":"Professional ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/image